race.comment: NIGHTLINE (11) produced a nice effort on debut in better company last start over 1200m at Gold Coast when second, beaten a head. Has plenty of upside so she will prove tough to beat. VINTAGE VIBES (14) returns and looks to have come on nicely during the break on the back of some nice trial performances. Draws to get the gun run from the inside pillar and can make the perfect return. VAN DE BAN (8) showed improvement second-up when closing off nicely into fifth. Backs up quickly and is open to further improvement. Holds claims. KOZAK PRINCE (2) returns from a break. Placed in a recent trial. Opened last campaign with a fourth at this track over 1200m. In the mix.
